"title": "7271: Zion, as a symbol",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7271",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Central to the life of the nation of Israel, it became the symbol of the whole nation and was seen, especially by the prophets, as the focus of God's promises and his final victory. In the NT Zion is a symbol of the new Israel, the church.</p>\n<h2>Zion as the dwelling-place of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:21\">PSA 135:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:2\">PSA 76:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:13-Ps132:14\">PSA 132:13–132:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:17\">JOL 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Zion as a symbol of God's people</h2>\n<h3>A symbol of Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:14\">PSA 9:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:1-Isa52:2\">ISA 52:1–52:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:8-Lam2:10\">LAM 2:8–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:6-Mic4:8\">MIC 4:6–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:5\">MAT 21:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:15\">JHN 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a></p>\n<h3>A symbol of Judah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:68\">PSA 78:68</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:19\">JER 14:19</a></p>\n<h3>A symbol of Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:1\">LAM 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:13\">ISA 46:13</a></p>\n<h2>Zion as the object of God's attention</h2>\n<h3>The object of God's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps87:2\">PSA 87:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:13-Ps102:16\">PSA 102:13–102:16</a></p>\n<h3>The object of God's blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps133:3\">PSA 133:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:13-Ps132:16\">PSA 132:13–132:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:12-Ps147:14\">PSA 147:12–147:14</a></p>\n<h3>The object of God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:18\">JER 26:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:12\">MIC 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:8-Isa1:9\">ISA 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:2-Jer6:5\">JER 6:2–6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:22-Jer6:23\">JER 6:22–6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:1-Joel2:2\">JOL 2:1–2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Zion as the focus of God's presence and promises</h2>\n<h3>The security of Zion because of God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:4-Ps46:7\">PSA 46:4–46:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:1-Ps48:14\">PSA 48:1–48:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps125:1-Ps125:2\">PSA 125:1–125:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:22-Isa37:23\">ISA 37:22–37:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:21-2Kgs19:22\">2KI 19:21–19:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:16\">JOL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>The restoration of Zion because of God's promises</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:17-Jer30:22\">JER 30:17–30:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:1-Ps126:3\">PSA 126:1–126:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:10-Jer29:14\">JER 29:10–29:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:38-Jer31:40\">JER 31:38–31:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:6-Mic4:7\">MIC 4:6–4:7</a></p>\n<h3>The salvation of Zion because of God's coming king and Saviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9-Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:9–9:10</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:5\">MAT 21:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:15\">JHN 12:15</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:11-Isa62:12\">ISA 62:11–62:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:8\">MIC 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Zion destined to be a city for all peoples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:21-Ps102:22\">PSA 102:21–102:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps87:4-Ps87:6\">PSA 87:4–87:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:2-Isa2:4\">ISA 2:2–2:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:1-Mic4:3\">MIC 4:1–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:3-Isa56:7\">ISA 56:3–56:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:16\">ZEC 14:16</a></p>\n<h2>Zion as an NT symbol of the new Israel, the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22-Heb12:23\">HEB 12:22–12:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:33\">ROM 9:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6\">1PE 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">ISA 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:16\">ISA 28:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:16\">HEB 11:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:1\">REV 14:1</a></p>",
